    This data adapter will handle all reading/writing concerns for storing and retrieving GeoTools SimpleFeature objects to and from a GeoWave persistent store in Accumulo.

    A GeoWave RowBuilder, used internally by AbstractDataAdapter to construct rows from a set field values (in this case SimpleFeatures from a set of attribute values).
